
CssSelector'un farkli kullanimlarini kod yazarak pratik etmistik.
Ama daha farkli kullanimlari mevcuttur.


Sibling-kardes olan elementleri locate edebilmek icin bazi ozel kullanimlar mevcuttur.




        first-child      - first child
        last-child       - last child
        nth-child()      - n. child
        nth-last-child() - sondan n. child


        #month>option+option+option
        #month>option:nth-child(3)
        #month>*:nth-child(3)
        #month>:nth-child(3)
        #month>:nth-last-child(10)
        #month>:last-child
        #month> option[selected='1'] +option


        first-of-type
        last-of-type
        nth-of-type()

        form#reg>input:first-of-type
        form#reg>input:last-of-type
        form#reg>input:nth-of-type(6)

         */